{% doc %}
  Global spacing tokens and utilities for LUSENA sections.

  CSS lives in assets/lusena-spacing.css (loaded as a standalone asset in
  layout/theme.liquid). This snippet is kept so existing {% render %} calls
  don't break and the doc stays discoverable.

  Provides:
  - tier spacing classes (`lusena-spacing--*`)
  - same-background section gap behavior
  - semantic intra-section gap classes (`lusena-gap-*`)
  - container-level content-flow utilities (`lusena-content-flow`, `lusena-content-flow--tight`, `lusena-content-flow--relaxed`)
{% enddoc %}

{%- comment -%}
  All CSS has been moved to assets/lusena-spacing.css to avoid
  the compiled_assets/styles.css size-limit truncation.
  This snippet is intentionally empty beyond this doc block.
{%- endcomment -%}
